{\b\fs28 Technical Specifications}\par
\par

{\b\fs24 Database Schema}\par
• {\b Users:} Authentication, profile information, roles\par
• {\b Properties:} Details, amenities, location, pricing\par
• {\b Bookings:} Rental periods, status, payment information\par
• {\b Reviews:} Ratings, comments, user references\par
\par

{\b\fs24 API Endpoints}\par
• Authentication: /api/auth/*\par
• Properties: /api/properties/*\par
• Bookings: /api/bookings/*\par
• Payments: /api/payments/*\par
• Admin: /api/admin/*\par
\par

{\b\fs24 Security Features}\par
• JWT-based authentication\par
• Input validation and sanitization\par
• CORS configuration\par
• Rate limiting\par
• Secure file uploads\par
\par

